{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \b \fs36 MIDI Choking Hazard\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Incoming notes choke (by note-off) up to four other notes.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 http://wiki.cockos.com/wiki/index.php/Jesusonic_Effects_Documentation#ChokingHazard\par}
}

