{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \b \fs36 MIDI KeyMap\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Incoming notes are transformed according to the data in the selected map file.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 http://wiki.cockos.com/wiki/index.php/Jesusonic_Effects_Documentation#KeyMap\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Note: Requires user defined key mapping files. A sample is provided in the package "Key map files for IX effects".\par}
}

