{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \b \fs36 MIDI Key Snap\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Out of key notes are either blocked or mapped to the nearest in key note.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 http://wiki.cockos.com/wiki/index.php/Jesusonic_Effects_Documentation#KeySnap\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Note: Requires user defined scale files. Samples are provided in the package "Scale files for IX effects".\par}
}

