\widowctrl\hyphauto

{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \b \fs36 MIDI Router\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 MIDI messages on input channel are diverted to the output channel. Can route notes, non-notes or all messages. Notes can be transposed.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 http://wiki.cockos.com/wiki/index.php/Jesusonic_Effects_Documentation#Router\par}
}

