{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \b \fs36 MIDI Variant\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Creates variation in incoming note messages. When triggered by the pattern, outputs a random note from the specified scale.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 http://wiki.cockos.com/wiki/index.php/Jesusonic_Effects_Documentation#Variant\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Note: Requires user defined scale and sequence files. Samples are provided in the packages "Scale files for IX effects" and "Sequence files for IX effects".\par}
}

